321 833 693 (Work Group:     Library Clause 24) 693 SB
321 889 480 ( Issue Number:   24-021) 480 SB
321 945 982 ( Title:          Separate Header for Stream Iterators) 982 SB
321 1001 347 ( Section:        24.4) 347 SB
321 1057 376 ( Status:         active) 376 SB
321 1113 261 ( Description:) 261 SB
321 1169 424 ( From public review:) 424 SB
321 1225 1399 (    Drawing iostream into an implementation that just needs iterators) 1399 SB
321 1281 461 (    is most unfortunate.) 461 SB
321 1393 1408 ( The current iterator header includes headers <ios> and <streambuf>) 1408 SB
321 1449 1265 ( to handle the stream iterators in 24.4.  This requires all of I/O) 1265 SB
321 1505 1320 ( to be included in the iterators header.  Yet I/O only needs this if) 1320 SB
321 1561 454 ( the iterators are used.) 454 SB
321 1673 1307 ( If a new header is used should it be in clause 24 or in clause 27?) 1307 SB
321 1729 935 ( Is <iositer> a good name for the new header?) 935 SB
321 1785 1434 ( Should the stream iterators be incorporated into current I/O headers?) 1434 SB
321 1897 441 ( From Nathan Myers:) 441 SB
321 1953 513 ( Message c++std-lib-4174) 513 SB
321 2009 1229 ( There are natural places for each of these iterator templates.) 1229 SB
321 2065 829 (   Move istream_iterator<> to <istream>.) 829 SB
321 2121 853 (   Move ostream_iterator<> to <ostream>.) 853 SB
321 2177 1514 (   Move istreambuf_iterator<> and ostreambuf_iterator<> to <streambuf>.) 1514 SB
321 2233 1046 (   Add forward declarations of all four to <iosfwd>.) 1046 SB
321 2345 746 ( Changes to be made would include:) 746 SB
321 2401 993 (  Move the stream iterators into the I/O headers.) 993 SB
321 2513 1275 (  Remove #include's for iosfwd, ios, and streambuf from 24.1.6) 1275 SB
321 2569 1189 (  [lib.iterator.tags] Header <iterator> synopsis and tags for) 1189 SB
321 2625 328 (  subclause 24.4.) 328 SB
321 2737 1405 (  Move istream_iterator to <istream>, ostream_iterator to <ostream>,) 1405 SB
321 2793 1210 (  and the streambuf iterators to <streambuf>.  Add forward) 1210 SB
321 2849 1329 (  declarations of all four to <iosfwd>.  Add #include <iterator> in) 1329 SB
